title: Widespread Panic - 2013.07.13 - The Joint, Las Vegas, NV
description:
Widespread Panic | 2013.07.13 | The Joint, Hard Rock Hotel, Las Vegas, NV
1: Henry Parsons Died, Surprise Valley, I'm Not Alone, Dirty Side Down, Wondering, Ribs And Whiskey, Pickin' Up The Pieces*, Can't Get High, Big Wooly Mammoth > Chilly Water
2: Saint Ex, Space Wrangler, Rebirtha > Impossible > Sell Sell > Drums > I Walk On Guilded Splinters**, Christmas Katie** > Slippin' Into Darkness***, Superstition
E: Many Rivers To Cross, The Take Out > Porch Song****
* with Kevin Harris on tenor saxophone, Roger Lewis on baritone saxophone
** with Dirty Dozen Brass Band on horns
*** with Dirty Dozen Brass Band on horns, Steve Lopez on percussion
**** with Carrot Top on percussion
[The Dirty Dozen Brass Band opened]
